item.title: Visit to Scripps Institution of Oceanography
item.description: Hajoon visited Bruce Cornuelle and Art Miller at Scripps Institution of Oceanography in February, 2020. The main purpose of the visit is to set up the WRF-MITgcm coupled model over the northwest Pacific.
